
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I select 'Yes' radio button in Contrast enhanced box on Page 03 of Thoracic MRT
And	I go to Page 05 of Thoracic MRT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Cystic fibrosis' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Quantitative, Eichinger score' radio button is enabled
And 'Descriptive' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Descriptive' radio button
Then 'Morphology I' tab is enabled and preselected
And 'Morphology II' tab is enabled
And 'Perfusion disorder' checkbox is enabled

When I am on 'Morphology I' tab
Then 'Bronchiectasis/Wall thickening' checkbox is enabled
And 'Mucus plaque' checkbox is enabled
And 'Sacculation/abscess' checkbox is enabled
And 'Consolidation' checkbox is enabled

When I click on 'Bronchiectasis/Wall thickening' checkbox
Then a multiple selection localizer is enabled

When I click on 'Mucus plaque' checkbox
Then a multiple selection localizer is enabled

When I click on 'Sacculation/abscess' checkbox
Then a multiple selection localizer is enabled

When I click on 'Consolidation' checkbox
Then a multiple selection localizer is enabled

When I click on 'Perfusion disorder' checkbox
Then a multiple selection localizer is enabled
